  "text": "Next, to determine whether Pdgfra is expressed in XEN cells, which represent the PrE lineage, we established XEN cell lines from the Pdgfra H2B-GFP strain. Live imaging has revealed that even though they are clonal, XEN cells exhibit heterogeneity in their morphology [CITATION_1] . The Pdgfra H2B-GFP reporter was expressed in all cells at equivalent levels (see Fig. 4E ), suggesting that Pdgfra is homogeneously expressed in XEN cells irrespective of morphological transitions.",
